Reporter
+ problem_type: regression or classification
+ leaderboard(): pd.DataFrame()
Performance metrics for final user on train set
+ regression: mse, mae, rmse, r^2
+ classification (binary): roc auc, precision, recall, f1 score + classification (multi): log loss, precision, recall, f1 score
Utilities for model persistence
+ hyperparameters and parameters of each model
+ serialized models (e.g. in pkl format)
